<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, September 1 (Xinhua) -- Russia will provide Kyrgyzstan
with arms, ammunition, Su-24 bombers and Su-25 fighters to help
the Central Asian nation to fight armed gunmen, the Interfax news
agency reported Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Russia has drawn up a series of steps for helping Kyrgyzstan in
its efforts to eliminate bandit formations in the southwestern
part of the country.
</P>
<P>
