<HEADLINE> Nigerian Army on Alert for President's Order to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, September 2 (Xinhua) -- Nigerian army said Wednesday it
had been already on the alert following the escalation of the
armed conflict between the Ilajes and the Arogbo-Ijaws in the
the troubled riverine area of Ondo State.
</P>
