Commission, said that these projects are important because they
will play a major role in boosting the local economy.
</P>
<P>
China has carried out a policy of increasing investment to
stimulate domestic demand since last year. Total investment in
fixed assets nationwide increased 15.1 percent in the first half
of this year to 668.7 billion yuan (about 80 billion U.S. dollars).
