success acclaimed across the world for its reform and opening
policy, as well as making great progress in the construction of a
democratic legal system," Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
"Administering state affairs in accordance with the law and
building a socialist country with the rule of law has become the
fundamental principle of China," Jiang wrote, stressing that the
Chinese people are struggling to build a strong, democratic,
civilized and modernized socialist country.
</P>
<P>
