<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, September 2 (Xinhua) -- Zambian President Frederick
Chiluba will head a cabinet committee to implement a drug
trafficking and abuse control master-plan.
</P>
<P>
Thursday's Zambia Daily Mail quoted Vice-President Christon
