Economic Cooperation (MOFTEC) Shi Guangsheng, MOFTEC Chief
Negotiator Long Yongtu, and Assistant Foreign Minister Wang
Guangya, who will attend the 11th APEC Ministerial Meeting, will
also attend the 7th APEC Informal Leadership Meeting as members of
