<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, September 2 (Xinhua) -- The Hongkong and Shanghai
Banking Corp. Ltd. (HSBC), a major subsidiary of British banking
giant HSBC Holdings plc, announced it had received approval from
the People's Bank of China to upgrade its representative office in
Guangzhou to full branch status.
</P>
<P>
The authorization from the People's Bank of China, the country'
s central bank, will bring the total number of HSBC's branches in
