minister, only keeping Logiin Tsog in an acting capacity.
</P>
<P>
State Great Hural voted to dismiss former prime minister
Narantsatsralt and his eight-month-old government on July 22 and
later elected Rinchinnyamiin Amarjargal as his successor on July
30. 
