<HEADLINE> French President Visits Canada </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, September 1 (Xinhua) -- French President Jacques Chirac
arrived here Wednesday afternoon for a week-long state visit to
Canada.
</P>
<P>
