The French president is expected at the 8th biannual Summit of
la Francophonie from September 3-5 in the eastern Atlantic city of
Moncton, New Brunswick.
</P>
<P>
On September 6, Chretien will accompany Chirac on a trip to the
far north territory of Nunavut. The French president ends his
visit the next day. 
